source.name: FY10_Life Insurance Payments, Face Value of Insurance, and Number of Policies
source.description: Fiscal Year 2010 life insurance payments, face value of Insurance, and total number of policies by state.  Data were derived from Actuarial reports, including FY 2010 Statement of Cash Flows, FY 2010 Policy Exhibit, and FY 2010 State of Residency Report.
